analysis indicated that CS (
6
) and BL are biosynthesized from a common phytosterol, campesterol (CR) (
3
), which has the same carbon skeleton as that of CS (
6
) and BL (Suzuki et al., 1993), suggesting that the biosynthesis of CS (
6
